results.name: Coefficients in expansion of E_6^(11/12).
comment: In general, for 0 < m < 1, the expansion of (E_6)^m is asymptotic to -m * Gamma(1/4)^(16*m) * 3^(2*m) * exp(2*Pi*n) / (2^(13*m) * Pi^(12*m) * Gamma(1-m) * n^(1+m)). - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Mar 05 2018
mathematica: nmax = 20; CoefficientList[Series[(1 - 504*Sum[DivisorSigma[5,k]*x^k, {k, 1, nmax}])^(11/12), {x, 0, nmax}], x] (* _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Jul 08 2017 *)
